# Hugging Face API Key (OPTIONAL - works without it!)
#
# The app works WITHOUT any API key using Hugging Face's free Inference API.
# Adding an API key gives you higher rate limits.
#
# How to get a FREE API key (optional):
# 1. Visit https://huggingface.co/join
# 2. Sign up for a free account
# 3. Go to https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# 4. Click "New token" → Create a "Read" token
# 5. Copy the token (starts with "hf_...")
#
# For local development (optional):
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder below with your token (or leave empty)
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control!
#
# For Vercel deployment (optional):
# 1. This is OPTIONAL - the app works without it
# 2. If you want higher rate limits:
#    - Go to Project Settings → Environment Variables
#    - Add HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY with your token
#
HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY=

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT NOTES:
# - The .env.local file is gitignored and will NOT be committed
# - NEVER commit API keys to version control
# - The app works perfectly WITHOUT any API key!
# - API key is only needed for higher rate limits (1000+ requests/day)
